  <brief_title>Icotinib in Advanced Non-small Cell Lung Cancer (NSCLC) With Hepatic Insufficiency</brief_title>
  <official_title>Safety Assessment of Icotinib in Advanced NSCLC Patients With Hepatic Insufficiency: A Multi-center, Open-label, Single-arm Study</official_title>
  <sponsors>
